Welcome to Mwenyi Safaris Lodge & Camp : Your Home in the Wild Nestled in the heart of the unspoilt African bush of Chirundu, Mwenyi Safaris Lodge offers an unparalleled experience that combines the beauty of nature with top-class amenities. Our lodge is the perfect retreat for those seeking tranquility, adventure, and a touch of luxury.




At Mwenyi Safaris Lodge, we provide a range of accommodation options designed to cater to your every need. From cozy, rustic cabins to luxurious suites, our rooms are equipped with modern amenities to ensure your stay is as comfortable as it is memorable. Wake up to the sounds of nature and enjoy stunning views of the African wilderness right from your window.







Mwenyi Safaris Lodge is also an ideal venue for business events and conferences. Our state-of-the-art facilities are equipped to host meetings, workshops, and corporate retreats. We offer tailored packages to ensure your event runs smoothly, providing everything from audio-visual equipment to catering services.










Our on-site restaurant offers a culinary journey through African and international cuisines. Using fresh, locally sourced ingredients, our chefs create mouth-watering dishes that are sure to delight your palate. Whether you prefer a hearty breakfast, a leisurely lunch, or an elegant dinner, our restaurant caters to all tastes and preferences.
